                    Tech draws are the most reliable way to gauge your chances
                    of invitation. Unlike general draws that fluctuate wildly,
                    tech draws have shown consistent patterns.
                </p>
                <div class="not-prose grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-6">
                    <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-indigo-900">Consistency</h4>
                        <p class="text-indigo-800 text-sm">
                            Draws happen almost every single Tuesday, except
                            holidays.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
